# Cross-origin isolation (COOP/COEP) — kept ON so EmulatorJS can use threads
# (SharedArrayBuffer) for the PS1 core. It is NOT what made the arcade iframe
# reload on minimize — that was the CSS `transform` in `.win.minimized`. The
# arcade window is now minimized via `display:none` (`.win-arcade.minimized`),
# which keeps the iframe (and the paused game) alive. COEP: credentialless lets
# cross-origin scripts/fonts/images (GSAP, Google Fonts, Unsplash) still load.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: credentialless

/arcade/*
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow
